snippet.title: Death Tapes - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Happy new year everyone ✨️! And with the start of this new year we are happy to share with you our teaser trailer for our new game DeathTapes
We are very excited to release the demo in the following weeks so everyone gets to experience it and give us feedback!
Have a great day and an amazing year💛💛💙💙

#teamherospunch #teamhp #DT #horrorgame #horror
